          • withDistributionUpToAmountUnderContract

            public AccountBuilder withDistributionUpToAmountUnderContract()
            Sets the accounts distribution limit type to "up to amount under contract". Use this setting when you want to allow pre-payment of charges (ie charges that are paid before the invoice that they are on is billed)

          • withDistributionUpToNextInvoice

            public AccountBuilder withDistributionUpToNextInvoice()
            Sets the accounts distribution limit type to "up to next invoice". Use this setting when you want to allow pre-payment of items on the next planned invoice. Planned charges that are on an invoice AFTER the next planned invoice will not get paid using this distribution limit.
